com.google.javascript.rhino.jstype

Interface StaticTypedSlot<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of information stored about the slot
    All Superinterfaces:
    StaticSlot
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Property, SimpleSlot, SymbolTable.Symbol, TypedVar

    public interface StaticTypedSlot<T>
extends StaticSlot
    The StaticTypedSlot interface must be implemented by variables that can appear as members of a StaticTypedScope.
